 Comparison of Data Mining Techniques, Journal of Computing in Civil Engineering (ASCE), 25 (3), 242-253. (SCI, IF=0.90)Chang, H. Y. and Chiu, C. K. 2011. Performance Assessment of Buckling Restrained Braces, Procedia Engineering, Vol. 14, 2187-2195. (EI)*Chang, H. Y. 2012. Seismic Risk Assessment for Steel FramedChiu, C. K., Jean, W. Y. , and Noguchi, T. 2011. Risk-Based Life-cycle Maintenance Strategies for Corroded RC Buildings Located in the Region with High Seismic Hazard, Structure and Infrastructure Engineering – Maintenance, Management,Life-cycle Design and Performance. (Online published) (SCI, IF=0.592)Chiu, C. K., Noguchi, T. and Kanematsu, M. 2010. Effects of Maintenance Strategies on the Life-cycle Performance and Cost of a Deteriorating RC Building with High-Seismic Hazard, Journal of Advanced Concrete Technology, 8 (2), 157-170. (SCI,IF=0.573)Chiu, C. K. and Jean, W. Y. 2010. Seismic Reliability Analysis of Reinforced Concrete Framed Buildings Attacked by Chloride, Journal of Architecture, 73, 51-68. (TSSCI)Chiu, C. K., Noguchi, T. and Kanematsu, M. 2008. Optimal Maintenance Plan for RC Members by Minimizing Life-Cycle Cost Including Deterioration Risk due to Carbonation,  Journal of Advanced Concrete Technology, 6 (3), 469-480.  (SCI, IF=0.573)Chiu, C. K., Noguchi, T., Kanematsu, M. and Nagai, H. 2008. Optimal Maintenance Plan of RC Building Damaged by Concrete Carbonation Using Immune Algorithm, Journal of Structural and Construction Engineering (Architectural Institute of Japan), 624, 173-180. (in Japanese)Chiu, C. K., Noguchi, T., Kanematsu, M. and Nagai, H. 2007. Optimal Maintenance Plan by Minimizing Life-cycle Cost Including Deterioration Risk Due to Chloride Attack, Journal of Structural and Construction Engineering (Architectural Institute of Japan), 616, 41-47. (in Japanese)Chiu, C. K., Noguchi, T., Kanematsu, M. and Nagai, H. 2007. Optimal Maintenance Plan by Minimizing Life-cycle Cost Including Deterioration Risk,  Proceedings of the Concre